<p>The Celebrity Big Brother star unveiled her impressive weight loss in jaw-dropping before-and-after photos recently, having undergone a 90-day transformation.  </p>

<p>She posted a snap of the impressive fitness overhaul alongside the caption: 'A little bit proud of myself guys! Not bad for reaching this goal after being stretched twice, having two babies in two years.</p>

